{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.4,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1001_00_01","textHome":"我叫环彩羽。因为刚来神滨市不久……@对神滨市了解的不是很透彻，@若是彼此间互有不熟悉的，希望能多多交流。@啊！话说……我的兴趣是做料理。@可以的话……我做晚饭给你吃好不好呀？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.9,"chara":[{"id":100100,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.9,"chara":[{"id":100100,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.1,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"id":100100,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.1,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":100100,"motion":100}]}],"group_10":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1001_00_18","textHome":"即使如今已经不是了，有朝一日@我也想向小忧坦白……曾经怯懦的自己。@因为我相信……小忧的话，@无论是怎样的我，都会温柔接纳的吧。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":7.1,"chara":[{"id":100100,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.3,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.1,"chara":[{"id":100100,"motion":100}]}],"group_11":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1001_00_19","textHome":"为了找回自己重要的东西……@我一定会一次又一次地变强！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.3,"chara":[{"id":100100,"motion":1}]}],"group_12":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_021.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1001_00_20","textHome":"接受弱小的自己……@从这里开始慢慢进步就好了吧……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.9,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":100100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.1,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":100}]}],"group_13":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.4,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1001_00_21","textHome":"开始一点点……慢慢改变了吗……？@即便厌恶过去的自己……也不能当作不存在……@应该接纳它，然后超越它……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.3,"chara":[{"id":100100,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.1,"chara":[{"id":100100,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"id":100100,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.8,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_021.exp.json","id":100100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.9,"chara":[{"id":100100,"motion":0}]}],"group_14":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.2,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1001_00_22","textHome":"和大家相遇之后，我终于明白了。@正因是重要的人，才不能隐藏自己的本心……@正因为重要，才必须传达出自己真实的心意。@因为对喜欢的人，是不应该说谎的……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.3,"chara":[{"id":100100,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.2,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_021.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.8,"chara":[{"id":100100,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":100100}]}],"group_15":[{"autoTurnFirst":6.9,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_021.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1001_00_23","textHome":"我不会再蒙混过关，也不会再欺骗自己了。@从自我保护的那层厚壳中飞出来后……@发现外面的世界好明亮，感觉浑身都轻松了。@我终于……成为了自己想要成为的人。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.7,"chara":[{"id":100100,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.1,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":100100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.3,"chara":[{"id":100100,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.8,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.2,"chara":[{"id":100100,"motion":100}]}],"group_16":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1001_53_24","textHome":"新年快乐。今年也请多多关照。为了能度过充@实的一年，要互相支持哦。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.4,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.8,"chara":[{"id":100100,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100100}]}],"group_17":[{"autoTurnFirst":7.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1001_53_25","textHome":"哇……就算是这个时间，新年的神社也相当人@满为患啊。嗯，没办法……慢慢地参拜吧！@啊，要去看看摊位吗？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":301}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":100}]}],"group_18":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.6,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1001_53_26","textHome":"八千代做了御节菜！要一起吃吗？啊，我也帮@了点忙。你看，这是我做得最满意的海带卷@！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":100100,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100100}]}],"group_19":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.6,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1001_53_27","textHome":"呜……感觉身体开始发冷了。回到家喝点热饮@吧？难得过年，甜米酒怎么样？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":100100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100100}]}],"group_2":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1001_00_03","textHome":"小忧她无论何时……@都有办法让大家露出笑容呢……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.2,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":100}]}],"group_20":[{"autoTurnFirst":6.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1001_53_28","textHome":"已经很晚了，这件振袖也该换下来了……但是@难得穿这一次，再穿一小会儿也好吧……？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":100100,"motion":301}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100100}]}],"group_21":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1001_53_29","textHome":"嗯……肚子饿了。但是忍住，忍住！过年的食@物都是高卡路里。啊但是，八千代做的御节@菜很好吃……呜……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_021.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":100100}]}],"group_22":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1001_53_30","textHome":"虽然希望一直有着这样愉快的心境……但不能@说出口。为了大家能过个安稳年……我必须@行动了！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_021.exp.json","id":100100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":100100,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"id":100100,"motion":400}]}],"group_23":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_021.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1001_53_31","textHome":"嗯，要去无尽镜界的话，先做好万全的准备吧@。大过年的，可不能让人看见狼狈的样子！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":7.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":200}]}],"group_24":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1001_53_32","textHome":"只要我们一起，就一定能克服各种困难。所以@不会有事的。为了过一个好年，大家齐心协@力吧！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":7.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":100}]}],"group_25":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1001_53_33","textHome":"爸爸妈妈在元旦发来了新年快乐的邮件。等他@们回来，就问问外国是怎样过新年的吧。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":7.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":100}]}],"group_26":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.2,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":301,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1001_53_34","textHome":"妈妈给我做了抽绳袋，正好配上这身振袖。但@是，没想到袋里还装了手工制作的发饰！因@为没告诉我，让我很惊讶！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.2,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100100}]}],"group_27":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.9,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":301,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1001_53_35","textHome":"今年的目标吗……想起来有好多……关于料理@的话，就是「钻研如何适当地调味」吧！现@在还总是做出口味寡淡的来……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_021.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_041.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":300}]}],"group_28":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1001_53_36","textHome":"八千代穿和服的样子，比往常还要更加成熟。@……我、我也看起来成熟点了吗？也是有化@了一点淡妆的……！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.6,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":100100}]}],"group_29":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1001_53_37","textHome":"除了年夜饭，鹤乃还送来了中式的炖菜和年糕@。都是油光发亮的一整套呢……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.2,"chara":[{"id":100100,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_041.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":200}]}],"group_3":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.9,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1001_00_04","textHome":"连我都开始说教别人了……@自己都有点难以置信……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.6,"chara":[{"id":100100,"motion":200}]}],"group_30":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1001_53_38","textHome":"三日月别墅的大家一起游玩了各种各样的新年活@动。菲莉希亚特别擅长打娃娃，而且还在积@极开发新技术哦。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":100100,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100100}]}],"group_31":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_041.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1001_53_39","textHome":"电视上的新年特别节目，会让人流连忘返 呢@。不知道什么时候莎奈也到了身边，两人就@这么看了两个小时。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":300}]}],"group_32":[{"autoTurnFirst":6.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1001_53_40","textHome":"想让住院的小忧也看看，是以前在医院外面放@风筝。虽然线缠到一起费了好大劲，但小忧@很开心，我也是……！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":301}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":0}]}],"group_33":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":401,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1001_53_41","textHome":"啊，在这！太好了……还在担心不知道跑哪里@去了……人开始多起来了，牵上我的手吧？@别走丢了。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.3,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":100100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":100100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.8,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100100,"